    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-b0d3a506-7fff-b1a7-2a72-fb7f6f5ab98d\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-indent:9pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">Prerequisites </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">Doppelganger</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-indent:9pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">Trigger </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">Something you can precisely detect (usually through vision) attempts an attack roll against you</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-indent:9pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">You alter your form just as the blow comes towards you, dodging away by growing away or withdrawing yourself from where the strike would land. You gain the Nimble Dodge feat and may use its reaction. You may select class feats that require nimble dodge as class feats without being a rogue, though you must satisfy any other requirement.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>"
